-MWvAEvrCgO6RMJiJsUO.text: Police and EMS are responding a report of a person who may have been shot at the Amstar gas station. The report is still unconfirmed.

-MWvB3lNoBObPIWtPmiw.text: Police have arrived at the scene.

-MWvDFUbBi9bHzOF469d.text: Police on scene report that a 17-year-old teenage boy sustained gunshot injuries at the scene. They also advise that they are shutting off traffic on North James Avenue toward West Broadway Avenue. The condition of the patient is still unclear.

-MWvDfhbp3_2X9GecgQb.text: Multiple Citizen users' videos show police at the scene.

-MWvE0RgyDjECEDHNq8K.text: Police on the scene also advise that they are shutting off traffic at the W Broadway Ave & N Knox Ave intersection.
